text:
What did Choucair say about & quot;
01 Nov 2019, 15:27 by Lebanon 24
The Minister of Communications in the caretaker government, Mohamed Choucair, said in a statement that Choucair telephoned Minister of Economy and Trade Mansour Btaish and discussed with him his request to price the recharge cards in Lebanese pounds. Communications can not do this, because the pricing of the cards issued by decree of the Council of Ministers, and that any change in this framework must be issued by another decree of the Council of Ministers. "The Information Office confirmed that" the official prices of the cards of all categories are still the same, "pointing "Network subscribers can You can also recharge their lines at the official rates through the websites of the two mobile phone companies: www.touch.com.lb, www.alfa.com.lb, or through the application "Alpha" and "Touch" or through ATMs. On the prices of the cards by visiting one of the following links: https://www.alfa.com.lb/en/prepaid/recharge,?https://www.touch.com.lb/autoforms/portal/touch/personal/prepaid / magic / tariffs ".
